# Zcash Open Development Lab (ZODL)
## Overview
**ZODL** (Zcash Open Development Lab) is a Zcash-powered mobile wallet application designed for financial sovereignty and privacy-first cryptocurrency transactions. The platform enables users to make private payments using shielded ZEC (Zcash) and facilitates cross-chain transactions to other cryptocurrencies.
ZODL represents a rebrand of the former **Zashi** wallet application, continuing its legacy with enhanced features and a renewed focus on mainstream adoption.
---
## Mission
> *"Bringing unstoppable private money to billions."*
ZODL aims to make cryptocurrency privacy accessible to mainstream users without requiring technical blockchain knowledge, empowering individuals with true financial freedom.
---
## Core Principles
| Principle | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Privacy** | Built from the ground up for shielded Zcash with best-in-class privacy as its foundation |
| **Self-Custody** | Users maintain complete control of their funds—no intermediaries or gatekeepers |
| **Consent** | Informed choice as a first-class principle, empowering users with information to make decisions |
| **No Tracking** | No collection of wallet activity, analytics, transaction history, or personal data |
