## Key Features
### ZEC-to-ZEC Payments
Private transactions using Zcash's shielded technology, keeping transaction details hidden on the blockchain while extending protection at the wallet level.
### CrossPay
Cross-chain payment functionality allowing users to send shielded ZEC while recipients receive their preferred asset (BTC, stablecoins, etc.), preserving sender privacy throughout the process.
### Swaps
Built-in private swap functionality powered by **NEAR Intents**, connecting Zcash to other crypto ecosystems without relying on centralized exchanges.
### Cold Storage Integration
Partnership with **Keystone Wallet**—the first hardware wallet to support shielded ZEC—offering air-gapped security for managing funds through the ZODL app.
### Real-World Purchases
Integration with **Flexa** enabling Zcash payments at major retail merchants including:
- GameStop
- Sheetz
- Chipotle
- And other participating retailers
### 1-Click Shielding
Instantly shield transparent ZEC received from exchanges with a single tap, converting public funds to private.
### Shielded Notes
Encrypted private messages that can be attached to transactions or sent independently, enabling secure communication alongside payments.
