## Development Team
ZODL was created by **original inventors and core protocol developers of Zcash**—described as "Zcash OGs" who established the standard for on-chain privacy. The team combines deep protocol expertise with product developers who previously redefined the Zcash user experience through the Zashi wallet.
---
## Transition from Zashi
ZODL is the successor brand to the **Zashi** wallet. Existing Zashi users will transition automatically to ZODL through a standard app update with no manual action required. All wallet data, balances, and settings are preserved during the transition.
